snippet: Tamika Catchings scored 23 points, including the winning free throws with eight seconds left, to give the Indiana Fever an 84-82 win over the visiting New York Liberty.
abstract: Indiana Fever defeat New York Liberty, 84-82; other professional basketball items noted.
